long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Quick way to switch from github to github1s and vice versa.
Open github repo with github1s in new tab and vice versa.

With github1s One second to read GitHub code with VS Code.
Usage
Just add 1s after github and press Enter in the browser address bar for any repository you want to read.
For example, try it on the VS Code repo: https://github.com/conwnet/github1s
